  "_meta": {
    "description": "Input scenarios for the TAXSIM-35 differential oracle harness. POSTed to https://taxsim.nber.org/taxsim35/redirect.cgi by tools/taxsim-refresh to populate taxsim-expected.json. The same scenarios are reconstructed inside DataManager by TaxsimOracleTests.swift for differential comparison.",
    "year_note": "TAXSIM-35 federal logic is coded through tax year 2023 only (it 404s/errors on year>=2024). We send year=2023 to TAXSIM and ALSO configure DataManager.profile.currentYear=2023 so both sides use 2023 law where possible. The engine's own 2023 tables may not be authoritative for all states, but using a common year minimizes year-mismatch noise.",
